## Stack

- **ESLint 10** with flat config: [`gui/pm-gantt/eslint.config.js`](../../gui/pm-gantt/eslint.config.js).
- React rules come from **`@eslint-react/eslint-plugin`** (`recommended-typescript` preset). Do **not** add `eslint-plugin-react-hooks` for ESLint 10 — it only peers through ESLint 9.
- Inline disables for hook/exhaustive-deps style rules use **`@eslint-react/...`** rule ids (not `react-hooks/...`).

## Verification

After changing files under `gui/pm-gantt/`:

```bash
cd gui/pm-gantt && npm ci && npm run lint && npm test && npm run build
```

Also run the Python dogfood gates from the repo root when the change touches shared contracts (see [`.cursor/rules/020-change-discipline.mdc`](020-change-discipline.mdc)).
